# LaTeX sweep-figure shadow copies.
# Authoritative sweep plots live in results/sweep_plots/ (generated by
# scripts/analyze_sweep.py); lexisflow_report.tex finds them via its graphicspath.
# Any sweep_*.png appearing under report_latex/figures/ is a stale duplicate.
